hint parseText "HOW TO USE<br/><br/>Setup your current radios with desired channel, volume, listening ear and PTT key. Then select <t color='#ffa4a4'>Save Radio Settings</t> -> <t color='#ffa4a4'>Confirm</t>.<br/><br/>The next time you load into the server select <t color='#98d7ff'>Restore Radio Settings</t> -> <t color='#98d7ff'>Confirm</t> to automatically load your previously saved channels, volumes, ears and PTTs.<br/><br/>Keep in mind you will need to carry the same types of radios in your inventory to restore the settings properly - only settings are restored, not the radios themselves. Select Show Radio Settings to see what Radio Settings were saved previously. The settings of a maximum of six radios can be saved.";